(349, 1, '2013-06-22 07:12:43', '2013-06-22 07:12:43', '<p>WNBA Champion and two-time All Star, Tammy Sutton-Brown has added author and speaker to her repertoire.<p>\r\n<p>Although born and raised Canadian she has spent more time living abroad than in her home town. Tammy believes that this exposure to various cultures, languages, traditions, and values enhance the quality of her life. This philosophy has motivated Tammy to travel extensively. She has visited more than forty countries across five continents.</p>\r\n<p>\r\nThroughout her travels Tammy was exposed to those more tested in life and was inspired to undertake the challenge of writing a children’s book series. Her series Cree and Scooter was written to encourage early literacy and getting children engaged in what they are reading.\r\nTammy speak to all ages and is driven by her dream of a world where all our children can read well.</p>', 'Tammy Sutton-Brown', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '199-revision-19', '', '', '2013-06-22 07:12:43', '2013-06-22 07:12:43', '', 199, 'http://biziindia.com/finaospeakers/199-revision-19/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
